High-level simplified model overview
Author: Jesse Morgan 2023
This chart is based on the work of (Joshua Leisk, Aline Noçon) on ME/CFS: Correcting Chronic Mitochondrial Dysfunction.
This chart abandons pure scientific accuracy in order to convey a simplified overview of concepts in the source material.
This may contain errors and inaccuracies. Please see original authors work for specific detail.
Note: the letters on each box are for easy discussion only, and do not denote any particular order.
